data.description: Welcome to "The Olivia Plan". Just 18 months young, this immaculate 2302 sq. ft., 3 br., 2 bath open floorplan home is loaded with upgrades including a whole house generator & closet factory closets! Sitting in a cul-de-sac lot this gorgeous home offers LVP flooring throughout all common areas, Kitchen with granite counter, bar counter, double pantry, custom soft close cabinets, farmhouse sink, tile backsplash & undercabinet lighting. The flowing concept of the kitchen & dining room through the family room is wonderful for entertaining with a double sided gas fireplace that looks through to the 12x15 stamped concrete screened in patio for added space. The primary bedroom with the large ensuite bath has a double comfort height granite vanity, large tile/glass shower, separate toilet and a walk in closet. A 2nd floor bonus/rec room with 150+ sq. ft. walk in attic storage, 1st floor tiled laundry room with built in cabinets & hanging ,2 car attached garage, stamped concrete walkway and rear patio, fenced in rear yard, Christmas lighting package and the list goes on.
